preference.name: HTMLStylesheetUnsupportedRenderingHints
preference.preference_description: Defines all of the rendering hints which are unsupported as HTML. If a hint in this list is encountered in an XRT file, then XRT is returned if the client supported XRT rendering. Otherwise, it is rendered as a string in HTML.
